{"tid":1732940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"圍魏救趙 唔係衝入包圍網！","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T23:57:24.000Z","uid":21997,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7724fb200d1e1201a13096042c7c02209b5f9d10","tid":1732940,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:50:22.000Z","msg":"我明大家心急救人，但係衣家尖沙咀已經完全被包圍，只係留番黨鐵同渡輪比大家出入。衣家集結尖沙咀絕對不智，對方一見時機成熟就可以cut鐵，到時更多人被圍係無地理優勢既尖沙咀街頭。<br />\n<br />\n圍魏救趙，係由外圍開始反包圍，唔係跳入對方包圍網呀！<br />\n<br />\n係各區食lunch 周圍開花呀！"},{"pid":"9e285e1a5bbe7f8569f982b0960449c384542fb0","tid":1732940,"uid":293673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bd3311edf8190a923b6e4477ed97a140c719a52","tid":1732940,"uid":13600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"請所有現任立法會議員及區議員（包候侯選人），立即聯合展開營救理大工作<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1732805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1732805</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"337967cb9fc42b7ad89f45dbfe96f0d8b955d29b","tid":1732940,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d707d68ba890d915631e032797b6a19c899e40","tid":1732940,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:07:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d1b75a42a4aa5893c422cd8893a641996e667a3","tid":1732940,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b63110d512aec5870a2ecfc683386375cc80328","tid":1732940,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:12:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"057ce46b8a9d919f26ba5ca31826af40fb5057c1","tid":1732940,"uid":326665,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"Poly 入面所有手足即刻拍短片，講定遺言，例如同父母道歉，同朋友道歉同道別咁。有咁慘得咁慘，喊得勁啲。<br />\n並堅決表明寧願餓死入面都唔會出來。叫人想像下成個poly 都係屍體嘅畫面，話係政府一手造成！<br />\n<br />\n香港人受軟唔受硬，如果有大量呢啲遺言短片，我相信相幾會會感動到香港人，喚醒到更多人企出來比壓力政府"},{"pid":"0a9499f924d04f7d588c5a97be64ae4fe32c313c","tid":1732940,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"外面手足各區食飯 令狗有後顧之休<br />\nPoly手足要盡打文宣戰 出悲情牌 對方越係要同Poly手足決戰 手足就越要避戰 拖得一時得一時 記得出現係Campus入面無罪架"},{"pid":"39d80c13e461d5e76c9530fd237924944738ab17","tid":1732940,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"292f3abedfda3d6f45ad662f108c43dc66455149","tid":1732940,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49253cc3439fc51b8abb73a535b8293d8bb831d","tid":1732940,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819a8b28a766b1b76d8823e11a6b39ad7fa88a07","tid":1732940,"uid":251083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c4a7ad1b6b8304214a07c2ac658ce3e81c10f6c","tid":1732940,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:31:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de922ed551588d8f451c117025dc9bc5daa1959e","tid":1732940,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d71d26ed79e338a13bfc955f7385310aeed427","tid":1732940,"uid":43179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"[正視聽] 小心風向撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1733006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1733006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"198b404a80fe6d5abad8e58ec4e7a610c01c2a5e","tid":173